<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p><strong><%=@resource.invited_by.first_name.capitalize%> <%=@resource.invited_by.last_name.capitalize%></strong> has invited you to view one of their MemoryBoxes at <%= root_url %>, you can accept it through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Accept invitation', accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @resource.invitation_token) %></p>

<%if @resource.invitation_message.present? %>
	<p>Invitation message:</p>
	<em><%= @resource.invitation_message %> </em>
<% end %>

<p> Once you have accepted the above invitation check the <%= link_to 'invitations', "#{root_url}/#/invitations" %> page to accept the MemoryBox invite.</p>

<p>If you don't want to accept the invitation, please ignore this email.<br />
Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your password.</p>

<p>Thanks!</p>
<p>The MemoryBox Team</p>